Key Match Events: The Suns took control of the game after the starters played until midway through the third quarter, outscoring the Nuggets by 13 points to secure a 118-114 victory.
Pre-Game Insights: Nuggets coach Michael Malone discussed the dynamic between Nikola Jokic and Russell Westbrook, noting their past tension and respect for each other.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Nuggets made some offseason changes, parting with key players from their 2023 championship squad, including Kentavious Caldwell-Pope and Reggie Jackson.
Others: Nikola Jokic tallied a near triple-double in almost 30 minutes played, with 21 points, 14 rebounds, and 9 assists.
